OL,5, An increasing number of people are     
OL,6, getting behind the wheel after using   
OL,7, cannabis and cocaine, according to one 
OL,8, of Britain's top police officers.      
OL,10,FChief constable Jo Shiner of the       
OL,11,FNational Police Chiefs Council said    
OL,12,Fthere was a "social acceptance"        
OL,13,Fparticularly among younger people.     
OL,15,FSome forces made more arrests for      
OL,16,Fdrug-driving than drink-driving during 
OL,17,FDecember crackdowns, the BBC has found.
OL,19,FThe Ministry of Justice said it was    
OL,20,Fclamping down on the behaviour.        
